rComments: Professor Salloum is one of my favourite profs at uOttawa. She genuinely cares about her students and puts in her best effort to make sure we succeed. Grading criteria was always clear and lectures were very helpful. Merci Madame!

Je l'ai eu comme prof de problèmes de français dans l'optique de la traduction et je l'ai adoré! Sa matière n'est pas la plus intéressante mais Sawson est très drôle et essaie vraiment de faire réussir ses élèves. Elle nous a donné un travail de rattrape quand la plupart ont eu une mauvaise note au premier exam. Très facile de passé si on étudie.

She is really nice, always wants to give students the best marks possible so long as they walk away having learned something. Tests are very true to the course material. Make sure and go to class to get the workbook answers, they aren't posted online and are very important for all tests!
Such a wonderful prof! Have her for my French translation classes. She's super nice, very clear, and hilarious!
